  ],
  "remarks": "General Director of Inspection Supervision and Performance Evaluation of Courts since Jun 2020. Former Prosecutor General of Qom (2008-2017) and former Head of the Directorate-General for prisons. He was responsible for the arbitrary detention and maltreatment of dozens of offenders in Qom. He was complicit in a grave violation of the right to due process, contributing to the excessive and increasing use of the death penalty and a sharp increase in executions in 2009/2010.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}